                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">3. Frictionless Listing Creation for Real Estate & Classified Ads</h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-sm mt-4">
                    <div class="bg-red-50/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-red-100">
                        <strong class="text-red-800 font-semibold block mb-1">The Friction (Traditional Way):</strong>
                        Listing a property or item for sale requires completing tedious multi-step submission wizards. Forcing sellers to scroll through nested administrative selects to declare their city, region, and district slows down the listing funnel, causing high user drop-off rates before submission completion.
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-green-50/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-100">
                        <strong class="text-green-800 font-semibold block mb-1">The Kettu Solution (Automatic UX):</strong>
                        Sellers simply choose their property location via a visual map container. Behind the scenes, Kettu instantly determines the matching sub-administrative administrative data (<code class="bg-white px-1 rounded font-mono text-xs">"fergana"</code> and <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded font-mono text-xs">"danghara"</code>). The platform maps the asset to correct search filter tags automatically, delivering clean data for searchers with zero friction for creators.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

